### 2. How many enqueue/dequeue operations are required to support the following sequence of stack operations?
```
push(10)
push(20)
pop()
push(30)
push(40)
pop()
```
- ❌ 8 enqueue 6 dequeue  
- ❌ 7 enqueue 6 dequeue
- ✅ 7 enqueue 5 dequeue
- ❌ 8 enqueue 5 dequeue

### 4. Three players, **X, Y, and Z**, participated in a football league. The ratio of the number of goals by **X to Y** and the ratio of the number of goals by **Y to Z** is **each 4:3**.They scored a **total of 400 goals** in the season. How many goals did **Player X** score?
- ❌ 144
- ✅ 172
- ❌ 128
- ❌ 160

### 5. A company’s financial team is analyzing the **stock capital as a percentage of total market value** over the past four years.

<p align="center">
<img src="data:image/png;base64,">
</p>

| Year               | 2018 | 2019 | 2020 | 2021 |
| ------------------ | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |
| Stock Capital ($M) | 50   | 70   | 90   | 120  |
| Market Value ($M)  | 1200 | 1500 | 1800 | 2100 |

In which year was the **stock capital as a percentage of market value** the highest?
- ❌ 2020
- ✅ 2021
- ❌ 2018
- ❌ 2019
